(38, 130, 'What will be the condition of accommodation while climbing?', '<p>During your stay in base camp, you will be provided a tent. You will also be provided food appropriate to your upcoming endeavor. Before you reach the base camp, you will be placed in a Hotel, lodge or tea house.</p>', NULL, NULL, 33, 'What-will-be-the-condition-of-accommodation-while-climbing', '1690546497558', NULL, '2023-07-28 21:59:57', '2023-07-28 21:59:57'),
