(44, 125, 'Connor Chilcoot', 'Chief Mountain guide', '<p>Connor grew up around the ocean and rocks of Southern California. After a few years of rock climbing, he was introduced to the mountains of the Sierra Nevada. His love for the mountains was realized following a winter ascent of Mt. Whitney. He found that challenging his physical and mental boundaries made him feel alive and at home atop these snow-covered peaks. Connor then left the warmth of Southern California and moved to Colorado where he spent his time ice and mixed climbing and recently siked from the top of Mera Peak (highest trekking Peak in Nepal. Through climbing Connor has found happiness and contentment, his focus is sharing this experience with others.</p>', '1724362118.jpg', 39, 'Tashi-Dorje-', '1690966266867', NULL, '2023-08-02 08:51:06', '2024-08-26 08:02:25'),
(45, 125, 'Lhakpa G Sherpa', 'Founder & Guide', '<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">Namaste and Tashi Delek Everyone!</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">I am from Solukhumbu District in Nepal! south of Everest. I belongs to a Sherpa family.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">It is my great pleasure to introduce \'Adventure Sherpa Tracks\' an emerging government licensed trekking and mountaineering company in Nepal run by Sherpa professionals with decades of experience in trekking and peak climbing activities . Adventure is in our gene since birth and we are here to offer you the best thing we do i.e. taking you around foothills of Himalayas, climbing peaks to reach the summit of snow capped mountains that blesses us with never seen before excellent panoramic </span>Himalayan views while sharing our inside stories blended with rich cultural and traditional values.</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">People have been travelling since long time to accomplish their desire. We are so lucky to have such a beautiful country naturally along with cultural and ethnical diversity. As period goes by, interest of travelers have increased from simple BUDGET TOUR to LUXURIOUS TRAVEL. A simple BUS DRIVE to expensive charter HELICOPTER FLIGHT. A simple few hour HIKING to three months long trek like GREAT HIMALAYAN TRAIL. A simple HILL WALK to difficult climbing attempt to World highest Mt. EVEREST. All different people around the World have different way and interest to explore our destination.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">Nowadays there are many different adventure travel companies in Nepal and it can be difficult to choose which one to go with. But if you are keen to travel in a familiar setting with an appropriate group size, experienced Sherpa guides ,where you get to interact and know the guides &amp; staff personally, you have come to the right place and we are Company who you can rely on.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">Me and my team am here to help all the travelers to make their dream of adventure in the Himalayas a lifetime experience.</span></p>', '1727869443.jpeg', 65, 'Muhammad-Ali-Ranja-', '1690966974668', 1, '2023-08-02 09:02:54', '2024-10-02 11:44:03'),
