(46, 'trekking', 'Mustang Region', 'The land of forbidden Kingdom', 'triplist', 'mustang-region', '1727892344.jpg', '', 'Mustang and Manang regions are famous for their rich Tibetan culture and deserted plateau surrounded by mountains. Touching the Tibetan borders, the region\'s lifestyle is heavily influenced by its neighbors. Buddhist domes and monasteries can be seen throughout the trail, while many populations still speak their native tongue and love to dress in their culture attire. More than just a beautiful landscape, Manang and Mustang are the epitomai of cultural exploration. \r\n\r\nThe forbidden kingdom of Lomanthang is situated in this region, surrounded by giant walls. As the region didn\'t want to be influenced by other cultures, the kingdom of Lo was restricted to outsiders until 1992. Now, it is considered one of the prominent tourist destinations where you can enjoy and learn about the mysteries of the area.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '6', '0', NULL, '2023-07-28 16:30:21', '2024-10-02 18:24:54'),
