hansi-theme-font: major-latin; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA; mso-no-proof: yes;\">Lightweight Long Underwear (2-3) Tops and bottoms. Capilene, other synthetic or wool. No Cotton (Mountain Hardwear Micro Power</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-left: .5in; text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l2 level1 lfo2; tab-stops: list .5in;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA; mso-no-proof: yes;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">·<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">         </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Cambria\',\'serif\'; mso-ascii-theme-font: major-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: major-latin; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA; mso-no-proof: yes;\">Stretch Tight &amp; Micro Power Stretch Zip T)</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-left: .5in; text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l2 level1 lfo2; tab-stops: list .5in;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA; mso-no-proof: yes;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">·<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">         </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Cambria\',\'serif\'; mso-ascii-theme-font: major-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: major-latin; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA; mso-no-proof: yes;\">Heavyweight Long Underwear. Top and bottom. Expedition weight Capilene (Mountain Hardwear Power Stretch Tight &amp; Zip T )</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-left: .5in; text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l2 level1 lfo2; tab-stops: list .5in;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: Symbol; mso-f