(1651, 148, '7', NULL, 'Trek to Dingboche', '4,410m', NULL, NULL, '- Continue trekking along the Imja Khola and pass through Pangboche village. Reach Dingboche, a beautiful village with stunning views of Lhotse, Island Peak, and other peaks.', 7, '2024-01-08 11:04:47', '2024-01-08 11:04:47'),
(1652, 148, '8', NULL, 'Acclimatization day in Dingboche', NULL, NULL, NULL, '- Rest and acclimatize in Dingboche. Take short hikes to higher altitudes to aid acclimatization and enjoy the surrounding mountain views.', 8, '2024-01-08 11:04:47', '2024-01-08 11:04:47'),
(1653, 148, '9', NULL, 'Trek to Pachermo Base Camp', '4,800m', NULL, NULL, '- Ascend towards Pachermo Base Camp, crossing moraines and rocky terrain. Set up camp at the base of Pachermo Peak and prepare for the climb.', 9, '2024-01-08 11:04:47', '2024-01-08 11:04:47'),
(1654, 148, '10-16', NULL, 'Climbing Pachermo Peak', '6,273m', NULL, NULL, '- This period is dedicated to climbing Pachermo Peak. The climb involves technical sections, including ice and rock climbing. The exact itinerary will depend on weather conditions and the climbing team\'s progress.', 10, '2024-01-08 11:04:47', '2024-01-08 11:04:47'),
(1655, 148, '17', NULL, 'Descend to Namche Bazaar', '3,440m', NULL, NULL, '- After a successful summit, descend back to Namche Bazaar. Rest and celebrate the achievement.', 11, '2024-01-08 11:04:47', '2024-01-08 11:04:47'),
