(1679, 150, '3', NULL, 'Kathmandu to Lukla to Chutanga', '2,860m and 3,430m', NULL, NULL, '- Fly from Kathmandu to Lukla, the gateway to the Everest region.\r\n- Trek to Chutanga, passing through beautiful landscapes and Sherpa villages.', 3, '2024-01-09 06:02:18', '2024-01-09 06:02:18'),
